      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/88a41a6c-a234-11e2-bdac-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  2 tests failed: recovery-small, conf-sanity.",
