        ]
      },
      "date": "2013-04-11 00:01:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/db0838cc-a236-11e2-9efc-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  1 tests failed: conf-sanity.",
